    "problemStatement": "You are given nnn numbers a1,a2,...ana_1,a_2, ... a_na1\u200b,a2\u200b,...an\u200b and another number xxx. Let P=p1,p2,...pnP= p_1,p_2,...p_nP=p1\u200b,p2\u200b,...pn\u200b be any permutation of  1,2,...n1,2,...n1,2,...n.\n\nYour task is to find the number of distinct values of ((((x%ap1)%ap2)%ap3...)%apn((((x\\%a_{p_1})\\%a_{p_2})\\%a_{p_3}...)\\%a_{p_n}((((x%ap1\u200b\u200b)%ap2\u200b\u200b)%ap3\u200b\u200b...)%apn\u200b\u200b\n\nInput:\nThe first line contains TTT, the number of testcases.\nThere are two lines in each testcase. The first line contains the numbers nnn and xxx.\nThe second line contains the nnn numbers a1,a2,...ana_1,a_2,...a_na1\u200b,a2\u200b,...an\u200b separated by spaces.\nOutput:Output in a single line the number of distinct values.",
